@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_unycce(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(v1)
    tmp = wp.abs(0.11)
    v2 = wp.abs(0.31)
    v1 = (v2 - (v1 - (tmp + 0.87 * v2 + 0.41)))
    v2 = (0.80 * v2)
    data[tid] = v0
